Package: r4subcore
Title: Core Contracts, Parsers, and Scoring Primitives
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R:
    person("Pawan Rama", "Mali", email = "prm@outlook.in",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7864-5819"))
Description: Foundational package in the R4SUB (R for Regulatory Submission)
    ecosystem. Defines the core evidence table schema, parsers, indicator
    abstractions, and scoring primitives needed to quantify clinical submission
    readiness. Provides a standardized contract for ingesting heterogeneous
    sources (validation outputs, metadata, traceability) into a single
    evidence framework.
